  "translations": {
    "en": "said to me Abu al-Hasan Musa son of Ja'far ( upon him be peace ) O! Hisham indeed Allah Blessed be and Most High gave glad tidings people of the intellect and the understanding in His Book so he said so give glad tidings My servants those who they listen the word so they follow the best of it those those who He guided them Allah and those they possessors of the minds",
    "ur": "said to me Abu al-Hasan Musa son of Ja'far ( upon him be peace ) اے Hisham بے شک Allah Blessed be اور Most High gave glad tidings people of the intellect اور the understanding میں His Book so he said so give glad tidings My servants those who they listen the word so they follow the best of it those those who He guided them Allah اور those they possessors of the minds",
    "tr": "said to me Abu al-Hasan Musa son of Ja'far ( upon him be peace ) ey Hisham muhakkak Allah Blessed be ve Most High gave glad tidings people of the intellect ve the understanding içinde His Book so he said so give glad tidings My servants those who they listen the word so they follow the best of it those those who He guided them Allah ve those they possessors of the minds",
    "fa": "said to me Abu al-Hasan Musa son of Ja'far ( upon him be peace ) ای Hisham به درستی Allah Blessed be و Most High gave glad tidings people of the intellect و the understanding در His Book so he said so give glad tidings My servants those who they listen the word so they follow the best of it those those who He guided them Allah و those they possessors of the minds",
    "id": "said to me Abu al-Hasan Musa son of Ja'far ( upon him be peace ) wahai Hisham sesungguhnya Allah Blessed be dan Most High gave glad tidings people of the intellect dan the understanding di dalam His Book so he said so give glad tidings My servants those who they listen the word so they follow the best of it those those who He guided them Allah dan those they possessors of the minds",
    "bn": "said to me Abu al-Hasan Musa son of Ja'far ( upon him be peace ) হে Hisham নিশ্চয়ই Allah Blessed be এবং Most High gave glad tidings people of the intellect এবং the understanding মধ্যে His Book so he said so give glad tidings My servants those who they listen the word so they follow the best of it those those who He guided them Allah এবং those they possessors of the minds",
    "es": "said to me Abu al-Hasan Musa son of Ja'far ( upon him be peace ) oh Hisham ciertamente Allah Blessed be y Most High gave glad tidings people of the intellect y the understanding en His Book so he said so give glad tidings My servants those who they listen the word so they follow the best of it those those who He guided them Allah y those they possessors of the minds",
    "fr": "said to me Abu al-Hasan Musa son of Ja'far ( upon him be peace ) ô Hisham certes Allah Blessed be et Most High gave glad tidings people of the intellect et the understanding dans His Book so he said so give glad tidings My servants those who they listen the word so they follow the best of it those those who He guided them Allah et those they possessors of the minds",
    "de": "said to me Abu al-Hasan Musa son of Ja'far ( upon him be peace ) o Hisham wahrlich Allah Blessed be und Most High gave glad tidings people of the intellect und the understanding in His Book so he said so give glad tidings My servants those who they listen the word so they follow the best of it those those who He guided them Allah und those they possessors of the minds",
    "ru": "said to me Abu al-Hasan Musa son of Ja'far ( upon him be peace ) о Hisham поистине Allah Blessed be и Most High gave glad tidings people of the intellect и the understanding в His Book so he said so give glad tidings My servants those who they listen the word so they follow the best of it those those who He guided them Allah и those they possessors of the minds",
    "zh": "said to me Abu al-Hasan Musa son of Ja'far ( upon him be peace ) 啊 Hisham 确实 Allah Blessed be 和 Most High gave glad tidings people of the intellect 和 the understanding 在 His Book so he said so give glad tidings My servants those who they listen the word so they follow the best of it those those who He guided them Allah 和 those they possessors of the minds"
